Definition: congenital disorder consisting of an inability to digest milk and milk products
Example: absence or deficiency of lactase results in an inability to hydrolyze lactose
Synonyms: lactase_deficiency, milk_intolerance, genetic_disease, congenital, disorder, consisting, of, an, inability, to, digest, milk, and, products, absence, or, deficiency, lactase, results, in, hydrolyze, lactose
Category: noun.state
